{"tid":1387752,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[警犬又無啦啦打人啦]","createTime":"2019-07-30T15:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T06:30:34.000Z","uid":168054,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"815b685b4718ef6da7b0a0d6419ec8f1e453d1d9","tid":1387752,"uid":168054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:03:26.000Z","msg":"葵芳警署有幾名保釋人仕從後門出黎，警察係十幾分鐘前已經叫家屬打電話出黎叫人唔到掟嘢，但根本冇人咁做，然後就有個律師出黎講同一番話後，幾名保釋人仕跟住幾名防暴警察一齊出黎<br />\n嗰幾名防暴警察用長盾推撞我地，做出所謂開路嘅動作，之前後開始打人，當我地陪同朋友離開警署一段距離後，已經聽到警察打人嘅聲音，途人尖叫嘅聲音，而巴士站長亦叫巴士即時離開總站，話有封路，而我眼見有狗跳上車頂兇人，啲人不停跑走<br />\n<br />\n到底我嘅家，香港，點解會變成咁，點解只係去接個朋友會變成，警察打人"},{"pid":"83f9b6048678f9d4fd3165b5ded82b406cc4fd05","tid":1387752,"uid":168054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:03:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f93792c905942d3393f7765c96731b5089a6e8b8","tid":1387752,"uid":168054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:03:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24ae2fa1aa54622a58ca222ae544c29bc0a08cd4","tid":1387752,"uid":287181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:06:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"022de184221a867ef36edcb942c6281edd230030","tid":1387752,"uid":168054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:06:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ffe360742959107c66371cf14fe9bcd2eee3f98","tid":1387752,"uid":168054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:07:28.000Z","msg":"警犬首先講大話話我地掟嘢"},{"pid":"2ce466f926be74e464ea18d4a7d743f55a845049","tid":1387752,"uid":168054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:08:10.000Z","msg":"繼而搵藉口出嚟打人"},{"pid":"dd47a996a9cf762295415d0bbdb67a6ef2b236fa","tid":1387752,"uid":168054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:08:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5aa17dc68d565b242dba19207dedc6ac69bf2ea4","tid":1387752,"uid":138981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:09:04.000Z","ms